<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />I am abandoned among the dead;</para>

<para style="q1">I am like the dead who lie in the grave,</para>

<para style="q1">about whom you care no more</para>

<para style="q1">because they are cut off from your power.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />You place me in the lowest part of the pit,</para>

<para style="q1">in the dark and deep places.</para>
